reviewText: The title says it all ,the cover picture alone is a good enough reason to buy it!

I just go this DVD after watching the TV ad which promised "Bikes, Broads, and Booze" and I can honestly say, I wasn't disapointed. First of all, the quality is amazing. It's shot in High Def so it looks really cool. The locations are all legendary for anyone that rides----Laconia, Daytonna, and Sturgis. but I especially like the bonus footage of the nudie girls in the desert. That was HOT!
